mainPackage
Class MetaMapConfiguration

java.lang.Object
  mainPackage.MetaMapConfiguration

public class MetaMapConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object

this class is a container for metamap configurations. All options configured by a user via a configuration file are hold in an instance of this class

more information about the configuration options can be found at: http://gate.ac.uk/sale/tao/splitch16.html#sec:misc-creole:metamap

Author:
Christian Hinterer
